      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on the new seasonal campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe. I need to nail down the core \"ideal consumer\" profile for our targeted ads. Can you help me build a detailed persona? I need stuff on their lifestyle, interests, their general cultural/ethnic background, and the kind of environments they hang out in to make sure the brand identity feels authentic and stays premium. Thanks.",
